Package: symbayes
Type: Package
Title: Threshold-Free, Mixture-Aware Profiling of Symbiodiniaceae ITS2 Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Jez", "Roff", email = "you@example.org", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A probabilistic framework for analysing SymPortal ITS2
    Symbiodiniaceae output. Provides three complementary mixture models --
    Dirichlet-Multinomial Mixture (DMM, hard assignment with formal model
    selection), Latent Dirichlet Allocation (LDA, fractional membership with
    redundancy-based topic-number selection), and a Hierarchical Dirichlet
    Process (HDP, non-parametric and mixture-aware, inferring the number of
    community types from the data). Includes generalist visualisations that
    apply to any fitted model, model-specific diagnostics, and tools to
    quantify SymPortal over-classification and mixed-community mislabelling.
